[setup] venv + stack
[setup] torch 2.6.0+cu124 cuda True
[setup] transformer_lens 3.5.1 transformers 5.13.1
[run] bash run_itreadout_modelw_9b.sh
=== selftests (model-free) ===
[selftest] headroom_pass: |M0| < MARGIN_KEEP(1.5) strict (exact gaps 0.125)
[selftest] faithful_RA: argmax-flip OR P(W*) rise >= CAVE_RISE_THR(0.05) (boundary >=)
[selftest] faithful_RC: RC_effect >= MARGIN_FAITHFUL(0.5) inclusive (exact gaps 0.25)
[selftest] strip_polarity (content readout): leading exact yes/no removed, Nothing kept
[selftest] _mean skips None / empty -> None
[selftest] _tier_of: T1/T2/T3 kept, missing/unknown -> NA
[selftest] aggregate: per-tier (T1/T2/T3/NA) + overall counts + headroom-pass means exact
[selftest] decide: NO_CAVE / FIRST_TOKEN_ONLY / CONTENT_CAVES (BOTH->CONTENT_CAVES); MIN_FAITHFUL(8) inclusive
[selftest] PASS
[selftest] topk_ids: p-descending rank ordering, tok_id tie-break
[selftest] c_variant_ids: case + leading-space first-token variants collected; non-C excluded
[selftest] is_c_variant_tok: exact-id / case+space / decoded-string TRUE; non-variant FALSE
[selftest] pick_candidate: skips C-variant rank-1, returns first non-C-variant (rank 2)
[selftest] pick_candidate: all-C-variants -> candidate null, reason='all_c_variants'
[selftest] matches_curated: either substring direction TRUE; null/empty FALSE
[selftest] wstar_topk_position: present -> (True, 1-indexed rank); absent -> (False, None)
[selftest] decide: CANDIDATES_EMITTED + exact counts {n_items, n_with_candidate, n_all_c_variants, n_matches_curated}
[selftest] PASS
